<div class="eyebrow">9-Minute Practice</div>
<h1>T'ai Chi Walking</h1>
<p class="subtitle">Fitness &middot; Flexibility &middot; Presence</p>

<div id="home-view">
  <div class="card">
    <div class="leaf">&#127807;</div>
    <p class="intro-title">Your Practice Awaits</p>
    <p class="intro-text">A 9-minute sequence blending classical t'ai chi movement with mindful walking. Find a clear, quiet space of 5&ndash;10 metres. Remove your shoes if possible. Move slowly. There is nowhere to rush to.</p>

